---

<PageLayout
  title="About Me"
  label="About"
  crumbs={[
    { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
    { label: 'About Me' }
  ]}
  sections={[
    { id: 'about-intro-section', label: 'Biography' },
    { id: 'panel-career-section', label: 'Career History' },
    { id: 'panel-skillset-section', label: 'Skillset Details' }
  ]}
>
  <article class="about-page">
    
    <!-- Section 1: Profile header (LinkedIn-style) + Intro + Links -->
    <section class="about-section-snap about-section--intro" id="about-intro-section">
      <!-- Dummy banner slider — swap in real personal photos later -->
      <header class="profile-header">
        <div class="profile-banner" aria-label="Personal photos">
          <div class="profile-banner__track">
            <div class="profile-banner__slide is-active" data-bi="0"><span class="profile-banner__tag">Photo 1</span></div>
            <div class="profile-banner__slide" data-bi="1"><span class="profile-banner__tag">Photo 2</span></div>
            <div class="profile-banner__slide" data-bi="2"><span class="profile-banner__tag">Photo 3</span></div>
            <div class="profile-banner__slide" data-bi="3"><span class="profile-banner__tag">Photo 4</span></div>
            <div class="profile-banner__slide" data-bi="4"><span class="profile-banner__tag">Photo 5</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="profile-banner__dots">
            <button class="profile-banner__dot is-active" data-bdot="0" aria-label="Photo 1" type="button"></button>
            <button class="profile-banner__dot" data-bdot="1" aria-label="Photo 2" type="button"></button>
            <button class="profile-banner__dot" data-bdot="2" aria-label="Photo 3" type="button"></button>
            <button class="profile-banner__dot" data-bdot="3" aria-label="Photo 4" type="button"></button>
            <button class="profile-banner__dot" data-bdot="4" aria-label="Photo 5" type="button"></button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="profile-meta">
          <div class="profile-id">
            <div class="profile-photo" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="profile-id__text">
              <h1 class="profile-name">Advaita Kelkar</h1>
              <p class="profile-role" data-scramble>Architectural Designer + Researcher</p>
              <p class="profile-degree">Master of Architecture · SCAD ’27 · Mumbai</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="about-bio">
        <div class="about-bio__text">
          <p>I’m Adi – Advaita Kelkar, a Master of Architecture student at the Savannah College of Art and Design (SCAD), with professional experience and interests spanning architecture, interior design, and web design. Hailing from Mumbai, India, my upbringing instilled in me a profound passion for design thinking and hands-on creation.</p>
          <p>I am driven by a commitment to continuous growth and collaboration, leveraging design’s transformative power to address challenges across creative domains. My problem-solving approach is multidimensional, drawing from a wide range of disciplines, and I find immense joy in the process of creation—always aiming to innovate and push boundaries.</p>
          <p>Throughout my journey, I’ve explored dynamic intersections between architecture, interior design, and web design, contributing to projects such as installations, exhibitions, and product design. Additionally, I curate content on computational design and AI, reflecting my keen interest in the intersection of technology and creativity.</p>
          <p>I believe in the limitless potential of design to overcome obstacles and inspire change, and I aspire to explore and create across all realms of creativity. Let’s connect and collaborate to shape impactful designs together.</p>
        </div>

        <nav class="about-bio__links" aria-label="Social links">
          <a href="https://instagram.com/advaitakelkar" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="about-bio__link">
            <span>Instagram</span>
            <svg class="about-bio__arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="miter"><line x1="6" y1="18" x2="18" y2="6"></line><polyline points="10 6 18 6 18 14"></polyline></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/advaitakelkar" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="about-bio__link">
            <span>LinkedIn</span>
            <svg class="about-bio__arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="miter"><line x1="6" y1="18" x2="18" y2="6"></line><polyline points="10 6 18 6 18 14"></polyline></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="mailto:advaitakelkar@gmail.com" class="about-bio__link">
            <span>Email</span>
            <svg class="about-bio__arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="miter"><line x1="6" y1="18" x2="18" y2="6"></line><polyline points="10 6 18 6 18 14"></polyline></svg>
          </a>
        </nav>
      </div>

      <div class="about-links" aria-label="Downloads and pages">
        <p class="about-links__note text-muted">Click on the links to access downloadable PDF versions</p>
        
        <a href="/advaita-kelkar-cv.pdf" class="about-link-row" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <span class="about-link-row__text">Curriculum Vitae</span>
          <span class="about-link-row__arrow" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg class="link-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="miter">
              <line x1="6" y1="18" x2="18" y2="6"></line>
              <polyline points="10 6 18 6 18 14"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>

        <a href="/advaita-kelkar-portfolio.pdf" class="about-link-row" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <span class="about-link-row__text">Portfolio</span>
          <span class="about-link-row__arrow" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg class="link-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="miter">
              <line x1="6" y1="18" x2="18" y2="6"></line>
              <polyline points="10 6 18 6 18 14"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>

        <a href="/projects" class="about-link-row">
          <span class="about-link-row__text">Projects</span>
          <span class="about-link-row__arrow" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg class="link-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="miter">
              <line x1="6" y1="18" x2="18" y2="6"></line>
              <polyline points="10 6 18 6 18 14"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 2: Career Tabs + Card Deck (Scrollable snaps) -->
    <section class="about-section-snap about-section--career" id="panel-career-section">
      <!-- Tabs (Sticky 100% width, equally spaced) -->
      <div class="about-tabs-container" role="tablist" aria-label="Career sections">
        <button class="about-tab-btn is-active" role="tab" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="panel-about" data-tab="about">About Me</button>
        <button class="about-tab-btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="panel-exhibitions" data-tab="exhibitions">Exhibitions</button>
        <button class="about-tab-btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="panel-timeline" data-tab="timeline">Timeline</button>
      </div>

      <p class="about-career__tagline text-muted">Dissolving roles and evolutions: Professional journey from Mumbai teams to SCAD fabrication, always fusing leadership with innovation.</p>

      <div class="about-tab-content">
        <!-- Panel 1: About Me (Experience) -->
        <div class="about-tab-panel is-active" id="panel-about" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-about">
          {experience.map((item, idx) => (
            <div class="about-card" style={`--card-index: ${idx};`}>
              <div class="about-card__details">
                <div class="about-card__top">
                  <span class="about-card__collab">{item.company}</span>
                  <span class="about-card__dot-sep">·</span>
                  <span class="about-card__tag-cat">{item.role}</span>
                  <span class="about-card__stacked-title">
                    <span class="about-card__dot-sep">·</span>
                    <span class="stacked-name">{item.title}</span>
                  </span>
                </div>
                <div class="about-card__mid">
                  <div class="about-card__header-row">
                    <h3 class="about-card__title">{item.title}</h3>
                    <span class="about-card__arrow" aria-hidden="true">
                      <svg class="link-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="miter">
                        <line x1="6" y1="18" x2="18" y2="6"></line>
                        <polyline points="10 6 18 6 18 14"></polyline>
                      </svg>
                    </span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="about-card__meta-grid">
                    <div class="meta-item">
                      <span class="meta-label text-muted">Dates</span>
                      <span class="meta-val">{item.dates}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="meta-item">
                      <span class="meta-label text-muted">Location</span>
                      <span class="meta-val">{item.location}</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="about-card__bottom">
                  <p class="about-card__desc text-muted">{item.desc}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <!-- Panel 2: Exhibitions -->
        <div class="about-tab-panel" id="panel-exhibitions" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-exhibitions" style="display: none;">
          {exhibitions.map((item, idx) => (
            <div class="about-card" style={`--card-index: ${idx};`}>
              <div class="about-card__details">
                <div class="about-card__top">
                  <span class="about-card__collab">{item.company}</span>
                  <span class="about-card__dot-sep">·</span>
                  <span class="about-card__tag-cat">{item.role}</span>
                  <span class="about-card__stacked-title">
                    <span class="about-card__dot-sep">·</span>
                    <span class="stacked-name">{item.title}</span>
                  </span>
                </div>
                <div class="about-card__mid">
                  <div class="about-card__header-row">
                    <h3 class="about-card__title">{item.title}</h3>
                    <span class="about-card__arrow" aria-hidden="true">
                      <svg class="link-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="miter">
                        <line x1="6" y1="18" x2="18" y2="6"></line>
                        <polyline points="10 6 18 6 18 14"></polyline>
                      </svg>
                    </span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="about-card__meta-grid">
                    <div class="meta-item">
                      <span class="meta-label text-muted">Dates</span>
                      <span class="meta-val">{item.dates}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="meta-item">
                      <span class="meta-label text-muted">Location</span>
                      <span class="meta-val">{item.location}</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="about-card__bottom">
                  <p class="about-card__desc text-muted">{item.desc}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <!-- Panel 3: Timeline -->
        <div class="about-tab-panel" id="panel-timeline" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-timeline" style="display: none;">
          {timeline.map((item, idx) => (
            <div class="about-card" style={`--card-index: ${idx};`}>
              <div class="about-card__details">
                <div class="about-card__top">
                  <span class="about-card__collab">{item.company}</span>
                  <span class="about-card__dot-sep">·</span>
                  <span class="about-card__tag-cat">{item.role}</span>
                  <span class="about-card__stacked-title">
                    <span class="about-card__dot-sep">·</span>
                    <span class="stacked-name">{item.title}</span>
                  </span>
                </div>
                <div class="about-card__mid">
                  <div class="about-card__header-row">
                    <h3 class="about-card__title">{item.title}</h3>
                    <span class="about-card__arrow" aria-hidden="true">
                      <svg class="link-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="miter">
                        <line x1="6" y1="18" x2="18" y2="6"></line>
                        <polyline points="10 6 18 6 18 14"></polyline>
                      </svg>
                    </span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="about-card__meta-grid">
                    <div class="meta-item">
                      <span class="meta-label text-muted">Dates</span>
                      <span class="meta-val">{item.dates}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="meta-item">
                      <span class="meta-label text-muted">Location</span>
                      <span class="meta-val">{item.location}</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="about-card__bottom">
                  <p class="about-card__desc text-muted">{item.desc}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 3: Skillset Section -->
    <section class="about-section-snap about-section--skillset" id="panel-skillset-section">
      <div class="skillset-header-row">
        <h2 class="skillset-title">Skillset</h2>
        <input
          type="search"
          id="skill-search"
          class="skillset-search-input"
          placeholder="Search skillset..."
          autocomplete="off"
          aria-label="Search skills"
        />
      </div>
      
      <p class="skillset-subtitle text-muted">A searchable interface that blends all projects—academic, work, free, and experiments—into one seamless digital archive for holistic discovery</p>

      <div class="skillset-grid">
        {skillsets.map((set) => (
          <div class="skillset-card" data-keywords={`${set.category} ${set.skills.join(' ')}`.toLowerCase()}>
            <h3 class="skillset-card__title">{set.category}</h3>
            <div class="skill-pills">
              {set.skills.map((skill) => (
                <a
                  href={`/projects?search=${encodeURIComponent(skill.replace(/\s*\(.*\)\s*/g, ''))}`}
                  class="skill-pill"
                  title={`Click to view projects using ${skill}`}
                >
                  {skill}
                </a>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  /* Snapping layout overrides */
  :global(html) {
    scroll-snap-type: y mandatory;
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
  }

  .about-page {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .about-section-snap {
    scroll-snap-align: start;
    height: 100dvh;
    min-height: 100dvh;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding-inline: var(--_tokens---space--small);
    transition: padding 0.3s ease;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-section--intro {
    justify-content: center;
    padding-top: 48px; /* space for fixed breadcrumbs */
  }

  /* ══ LinkedIn-style profile header ══════════════════════════ */
  .profile-header {
    width: 100%;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .profile-banner {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: clamp(110px, 16vh, 180px);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--_tokens---color--fg) 6%, transparent);
  }

  .profile-banner__track { position: absolute; inset: 0; }

  .profile-banner__slide {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.9s ease;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    padding: 12px;
  }

  .profile-banner__slide.is-active { opacity: 1; }

  /* Dummy gradient placeholders — replace with real photos */
  .profile-banner__slide[data-bi="0"] { background: linear-gradient(120deg, #2d3a5e, #5b7fa6); }
  .profile-banner__slide[data-bi="1"] { background: linear-gradient(120deg, #34564a, #6fae8d); }
  .profile-banner__slide[data-bi="2"] { background: linear-gradient(120deg, #5e3a4a, #a66b80); }
  .profile-banner__slide[data-bi="3"] { background: linear-gradient(120deg, #5e503a, #aa9a6b); }
  .profile-banner__slide[data-bi="4"] { background: linear-gradient(120deg, #3a4f5e, #6b97ae); }

  .profile-banner__tag {
    font-family: var(--_tokens---font--mono);
    font-size: 0.58rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.22);
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 999px;
  }

  .profile-banner__dots {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 10px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .profile-banner__dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: none;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0;
    transition: background-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }

  .profile-banner__dot.is-active { background: #fff; transform: scale(1.3); }

  .profile-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: -32px;
    padding-inline: 6px;
  }

  .profile-id {
    display: flex;
